*.wasm
.DS_Store
dist/
# Upstream Pyret checkout lives OUTSIDE the repo at ../pyret (clone of
# github.com/brownplt/pyret-lang into ../pyret/lang) so git ops here can't delete it;
# `pyret` is a gitignored symlink -> ../pyret. Our editable copies live in
# self-compiler/ and test-corpus/. Leading slash ignores the symlink AND any dir.
/pyret
